---

<MainLayout sd={structuredData} title="Return Policy | Lovosis Technology L.L.C" description="We are a leading bulk quantity exporter of security surveillance equipment based in the United Arab Emirates, specializing in wholesale distribution of top-tier CCTV and security camera systems."canonical={canonicalUrl}>

  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto p-12 border-2 m-12" >
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white  mb-6">Return Policy | Lovosis Technology L.L.C</h1>
    
    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2 dark:text-white">Return Window</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-white">
        We offer a <span class="font-semibold dark:text-white">7-day return policy</span> for our security system products. You may request a return within 7 days of receiving your item.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2 dark:text-white">Return Eligibility</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 space-y-1 dark:text-white">
        <li>Items must be unused, uninstalled, and in original condition</li>
        <li>Products must include all original accessories and packaging</li>
        <li>Proof of purchase is required</li>
        <li>Custom-configured systems are non-returnable</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2 dark:text-white">How to Start a Return</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-white">
        To initiate a return, email us at <a href="mailto:sales@lovosis.com" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">sales@lovosis.com</a> with your order number, reason for return, and any supporting photos.
        We will issue a Return Authorization Number (RAN) and provide return instructions.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2 dark:text-white">Non-Returnable Items</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 space-y-1 dark:text-white">
        <li>Installed or used products</li>
        <li>Items missing parts or packaging</li>
        <li>Customized kits or software licenses</li>
        <li>Clearance or promotional items</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2 dark:text-white">Damaged or Defective Items</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-white">
        If your item is damaged or defective, report it within 48 hours of delivery. Include photos or videos, and we will arrange a replacement or refund.
      </p>
    </section>

     <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2 dark:text-white">International Returns</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-white">
        International customers are responsible for return shipping and duties unless the return is due to our error. Mark packages as ‚ÄúReturned Goods‚Äù to avoid customs delays.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2 dark:text-white">Refunds</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-white">
        Approved returns are refunded to the original payment method within 10‚Äì15 business days. Contact us if your refund hasn't been processed after 15 days.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2 dark:text-white">Contact Us</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-white">
